===Mid-range=== * {{sleep | name=Arco dei Tolomei | alt= | url=https://www.bbarcodeitolomei.com/ | email=info@bbarcodeitolomei.com | address=Via dell'Arco dei Tolomei 27 | lat=41.888805 | long=12.476335 | directions= | phone=+39 06 5832 0819 | tollfree= | fax=+39 06 589 9703 | checkin= | checkout= | price=€190-220 | content=All the rooms come with private bath and shower. }} * {{sleep | name=Grand Hotel Gianicolo Rome | alt= | url=https://www.grandhotelgianicolo.it/ | email= | address=Viale delle Mura Gianicolense 107 | lat=41.887723 | long=12.460823 | directions= | phone=+39 06 58333405 | tollfree= | fax=+39 06 58179434 | checkin= | checkout= | price=Single €140, double €170 | content=Four star accommodation with twin, double with jacuzzi, triple and dus (double for single use). All with private bath and shower. Swimming pool, a private garden and a fantastic panoramic view of Rome. }} * {{sleep | name=Hotel Santa Maria | alt= | url=http://www.htlsantamaria.com/english/index.htm | email= | address=Vicolo del Piede 2 | lat=41.890133 | long=12.470046 | directions= | phone= | tollfree= | checkin= | checkout= | price=€160-230 | content=Gated hotel just off Piazza Santa Maria. Comfortable and has a nice courtyard. }} * {{sleep | name=Hotel Villa della Fonte | alt= | url=http://www.villafonte.com/ | email=info@villafonte.com | address=Via della Fonte d'Olio 8 | lat=41.890048 | long=12.470043 | directions= | phone=+39 06 580 3797 | tollfree= | fax=+39 06 580 3796 | checkin= | checkout= | price=€150-180 | content=Small hotel, all rooms have a private bath, free Wi-Fi, satelliteTV and A/C. }} * {{sleep | name=WRH Trastevere | alt= | url=http://www.wrh-trastevere.com/ | email=info@wrh-trastevere.com | address=Via di San Crisogono, 40 | lat=41.88786 | long=12.47432 | directions= | phone=+39 06 580 6344 | tollfree= | fax=+39 06 9670 8681 | checkin=13:00 | checkout=11:00 | price=€79-166 (low season-high season) | content=Friendly modern & minimalist guesthouse. }} * {{sleep | name=Hotel Parrasio | alt= | url=https://www.hotelparrasio.com/ | email= | address=Salita del Bosco Parrasio, 5 | lat=41.889613 | long=12.465721 | directions= | phone=+39 0694517620 | tollfree= | checkin= | checkout= | price=€95-261 (low season-high season) | lastedit=2023-02-26 | content= }}
